          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "When should I take AminoLean MAX Pre Workout?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>You can take AminoLean 20-30 minutes before your workout for a high-intensity pre workout boost.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15515210973229__65ec616c-ec79-4a60-9bd9-0322c651d7a9-1678419778126fd085-1": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How much caffeine is in one scoop?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>There is 250mg of caffeine in one scoop.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15515210973229__65ec616c-ec79-4a60-9bd9-0322c651d7a9-1678419778126fd085-2": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How many scoops should I take?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>The recommendation is to only take one scoop of AminoLean MAX.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15515210973229__65ec616c-ec79-4a60-9bd9-0322c651d7a9-1678419778126fd085-3": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Will it make me feel tingly or \"itchy\"?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes, there is a possibility that you could feel tingly from AminoLean MAX Pre Workout. This is highly dependent on your tolerance for beta-alanine.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "10f09184-b916-445c-b3ed-f2754925a17b": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What makes AminoLean MAX Pre Workout different from other AminoLean products?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>AminoLean MAX is our highest-stim pre workout. It contains Nitrosigine and beta-alanine, which maximizes pumps and makes your workout more intense, as well as nootropics for focus. AminoLean MAX has the most caffeine of any AminoLean product, at 250mg. </p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
